parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Power Tailgate Failure due to Water Damage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power tailgate can cause the tailgate to open or close randomly, leading to accidents or injuries, especially when driving with children or cargo on board. Water damage to the control module can also cause electrical system malfunctions, affecting the vehicle's overall safety and performance.
symptoms: The tailgate opens or closes randomly
the tailgate does not open or close
water leakage into the control module

and problems with the blind spot system
